        <div class="two-third individual-content">
            <h2>Meet Michael</h2>
            <h4>Born June 2006</h4>
            <p><span style="line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="https://www.hckids.org/wp-content/uploads/Michael-3-10-2014.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-2644 alignright" src="https://www.hckids.org/wp-content/uploads/Michael-3-10-2014.jpg" alt="Michael 3 10-2014" width="320" height="373" /></a>Michael loves superheroes and shares many qualities with them. He is a very intelligent, energetic and charismatic little boy. Like any good super hero, Michael needs a family that can teach him how to direct these qualities into something positive.</span></p>
<p>Michael loves to play outside and is good with electronics. When playing outside, he loves riding his bike, kicking around a soccer ball and playing pretend. When Michael is inside, he likes to play video games; <em>Minecraft</em> is his favorite.</p>
<p>Michael loves attention and thrives in an environment that provides structure, routine and boundaries. Michael struggles with his emotions when he is upset and needs a family that can model and teach him appropriate outlets for these emotions. Michael needs a super family to help him turn into the superhero he longs to be.</p>

